cdata.name: Big Data Block
cdata.desc:
Big Data Block is a Big Data (large volume of data) analysis platform. It provides the users with A.I-based tools to make a structured data treatment in order tooptimize the Big Data usage within their projects. In addition,Big Data Block enablesthe access to a marketplace tomatch the platform users with technical support experts.

The BDB token is an Ethereum-based (ERC20) cryptocurrency.Itis a utility token, it will powerthe Big Data Block platform, and serveas a medium of reward miners.
